'''Terence Dean "Terry" Brooks''' is a fantasy fiction writer and the author of the [[Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace (novelization)|''Star Wars'': Episode I ''The Phantom Menace'' novelization]]. He writes mainly epic fantasy,<ref name="officialsite">{{WebCite|url=http://www.terrybrooks.net/novels/index.html|text=Novels|work=[http://www.terrybrooks.net terrybrooks.net]|archivedate=20081221062814}}</ref> and has also written one movie novelization in addition to the [[Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace (novelization)|''The Phantom Menace'']]. He has written 22 [[Wikipedia:New York Times Best Seller List|''New York Times'' bestsellers]] during his writing career,<ref name="officialsite" /> and is one of the biggest-selling living fantasy writers.<ref>{{WebCite|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/6727885.stm|text=Studio plans Shannara film series|date=2007-06-06|work=[[Wikipedia:BBC News|BBC News]]|archivedate=20150907192001}}</ref>

